2018年6月11日，时任[[马来西亚首相|马来西亚首相]][[马哈迪·莫哈末|马哈迪·莫哈末]]對於[[2018年朝美首脑会晤|朝美首脑会晤]]表示歡迎，並表示世界不應對[[金正恩|金正恩]]懷疑並應學習他對於和平的期盼<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.my/dr-mahathir-praises-kim-jong-un-new-attitude-decision-trump-world-learn/|title=Malaysia PM Mahathir says the world can learn from Kim Jong Un’s ‘new attitude’ and decision to meet Trump|author=Jonathan Loh|publisher=Business Insider|date=12 June 2018|accessdate=15 June 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615083238/https://www.businessinsider.my/dr-mahathir-praises-kim-jong-un-new-attitude-decision-trump-world-learn/|archive-date=2018-06-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在[[東京|東京]]的一個記者會上， 馬哈迪希望朝美首次峰會能取得好結果<ref>{{cite web|title=Malaysia, Japan hope for successful US – North Korea summit|work=Bernama|publisher=New Straits Times|date=12 June 2018|accessdate=15 June 2018|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615111037/https://www.nst.com.my/news/nation/2018/06/379164/malaysia-japan-hope-successful-us-north-korea-summit|archive-date=15 June 2018}}</ref>，並表示馬來西亞重開北韓駐當地大使館，改善因金正男遇刺而低落的兩國關係<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-malaysia/malaysia-to-reopen-embassy-in-north-korea-mahathir-idUSKBN1J80O2|title=Malaysia to reopen embassy in North Korea: Mahathir|author1=Praveen Menon|author2=Darren Schuettler|publisher=Reuters|date=12 June 2018|accessdate=15 June 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614224658/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-malaysia/malaysia-to-reopen-embassy-in-north-korea-mahathir-idUSKBN1J80O2|archive-date=2018-06-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

